标题：长枪、矛（spear, lance）</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">经文出处</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-sets\">\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：חֲנִית</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：chanith)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam13:19\">1SA 13:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam13:22\">1SA 13:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam17:7\">1SA 17:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam17:7\">1SA 17:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam17:45\">1SA 17:45</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam17:47\">1SA 17:47</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam18:10\">1SA 18:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam18:11\">1SA 18:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam19:9\">1SA 19:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam19:10\">1SA 19:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam19:10\">1SA 19:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam20:33\">1SA 20:33</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam21:9\">1SA 21:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam22:6\">1SA 22:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam26:8\">1SA 26:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam26:12\">1SA 26:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam26:16\">1SA 26:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam26:22\">1SA 26:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam26:22\">1SA 26:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam1:6\">2SA 1:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam2:23\">2SA 2:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam2:23\">2SA 2:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam21:19\">2SA 21:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam23:7\">2SA 23:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam23:18\">2SA 23:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam23:21\">2SA 23:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam23:21\">2SA 23:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam23:21\">2SA 23:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs11:10\">2KI 11:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr11:11\">1CH 11:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr11:20\">1CH 11:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr11:23\">1CH 11:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr11:23\">1CH 11:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr11:23\">1CH 11:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr12:35\">1CH 12:35</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr20:5\">1CH 20:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr23:9\">2CH 23:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job39:23\">JOB 39:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job41:18\">JOB 41:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps35:3\">PSA 35:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps46:10\">PSA 46:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps57:5\">PSA 57:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa2:4\">ISA 2:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic4:3\">MIC 4:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Nah3:3\">NAM 3:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab3:11\">HAB 3:11</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：רֹמַח</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：romach)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num25:7\">NUM 25:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg5:8\">JDG 5:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs18:28\">1KI 18:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr12:9\">1CH 12:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr12:25\">1CH 12:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr11:12\">2CH 11:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr14:7\">2CH 14:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr25:5\">2CH 25:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr26:14\">2CH 26:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh4:7\">NEH 4:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh4:10\">NEH 4:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh4:15\">NEH 4:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer46:4\">JER 46:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek39:9\">EZK 39:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel4:10\">JOL 4:10</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：שֵׁבֶט</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：shevet)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam18:14\">2SA 18:14</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希：γαῖσος</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：gaisos)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jdt9:7\">JDT 9:7</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希：δεξιολάβος</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：dexiolabos)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts23:23\">ACT 23:23</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希：δορά, δόρυ</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：dora, doru)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jdt7:10\">JDT 7:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jdt11:2\">JDT 11:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/EsthGr8:12\">ESG 8:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Sir29:13\">SIR 29:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/3Macc3:15\">3MA 3:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/3Macc5:43\">3MA 5:43</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/3Macc6:5\">3MA 6:5</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希：κάμαξ</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：kamax)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Macc5:3\">2MA 5:3</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希：κέντρον</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：kentron)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/4Macc14:19\">4MA 14:19</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希：λόγχη</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：logchē)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John19:34\">JHN 19:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Macc5:2\">2MA 5:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Macc15:11\">2MA 15:11</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希：σιβύνη</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：sibunē (zibunē))</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jdt1:15\">JDT 1:15</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Latin</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">拉：framea</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Esd13:9\">2ES 13:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Esd13:28\">2ES 13:28</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">描述</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>在一根长而直的杆棒上面安装一个锐利的尖端，就做成了长枪，主要攻击方式是刺。枪杆的粗细略小于人手的虎口长度，长度差不多是一个人的身高或者更长。枪杆一般木制，配上金属枪头或枪尖（参<a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">2.5.1 枪头(spearhead)&lt;REALIA:2.5.1&gt;</a> ）。枪的尾端（枪纂）也用金属包裹，带尖（参<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam2:23\">2SA 2:23</a> ），可以用来把枪戳在地上，或者用作刺棒来驱赶牲畜。</p>\n<p>参<a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">2.3.1 鞘(sheath, scabbard)&lt;REALIA:2.3.1&gt;</a> 中的插图。</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">用途</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>打仗时，持枪的人握着枪杆的中间部位，用力刺向敌人，只偶尔用抛掷的方式来攻击对方（参<a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">2.6 投枪、标枪、短枪 (javelin)&lt;REALIA:2.6&gt;</a> ）。</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">翻译</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>翻译者在选择字词或短语时，应该尽量表明枪是一种用手握持和用来戳刺的武器（就像一柄固定在棍棒末端的刀那样使用），而不是通过投掷来伤敌。</p>\n<p>短语“举起他的枪”出现在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam23:18\">2SA 23:18</a> 和<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr11:11\">1CH 11:11</a> 。译作“他持枪作战”（<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Good News Translation (1992)\">GNT</abbr> 直译）意思是正确的。</p>\n<p>希腊文<em>dexiolabos</em> 在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts23:23\">ACT 23:23</a> 的意思不能确定，大多数译本将其译成“长枪手”（“spearmen”；<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Revised Standard Version (1952)\">RSV</abbr> 、<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New International Version (1984)\">NIV</abbr> ）、“持枪的歩兵”（“foot soldiers with spears”；<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Contemporary English Version\">CEV</abbr> ）、“持枪的人”（“men with spears”；<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New Century Version\">NCV</abbr> ），或“轻装备部队”（“light-armed troops”；<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Revised English Bible (1989)\">REB</abbr> ）。</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
